prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "Transition from Door Shut to Door Open when user opens the door",
      "evidence_quote": "The statechart transitions into the Door Open state."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Transition from Door Open to Door Open with Item when user places an item in the oven",
      "evidence_quote": "causing the statechart to transition into the Door Open with Item state"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Transition from Door Open with Item to Door Shut with Item when user closes the door",
      "evidence_quote": "the statechart then transitions into the Door Shut with Item state"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Enter Ready to Cook state after user inputs cooking time",
      "evidence_quote": "After the user inputs the cooking time, the Ready to Cook state is entered."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Transition from Ready to Cook to Cooking when user presses Start button",
      "evidence_quote": "the user presses the Start button, which causes the statechart to transition into the Cooking state"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Leave Cooking state and reenter Door Shut with Item when timer expires",
      "evidence_quote": "When the timer expires, the statechart leaves the Cooking state and reenters the Door Shut with Item state"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Transition from Cooking to Door Open with Item if door is opened during cooking",
      "evidence_quote": "If instead the door were opened during cooking, the statechart would enter the Door Open with Item state"
    }
  ]
}

